& H_{12}=\langle 1| H_{0}+H^{\prime}|2\rangle=\langle n| H_{0}+H^{\prime}|\bar{n}\rangle=\alpha \\
& H_{21}=H_{12}^{*}=\alpha \\
& H_{22}=\langle 2| H_{0}+H^{\prime}|2\rangle=\langle\bar{n}| H_{0}+H^{\prime}|\bar{n}\rangle=m c^{2}
\end{aligned}
$$

The stationary state equation is

$$
H|\psi\rangle=E|\psi\rangle
$$

or

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
m c^{2} & \alpha \\
\alpha & m c^{2}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
c_{1} \\
c_{2}
\end{pmatrix}
=E
\begin{pmatrix}
c_{1} \\
c_{2}
\end{pmatrix}
$$

