B=\left\langle\psi_{2} \mid \psi(0)\right\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}(1,-1)\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\
