\begin{equation*}
H=E_{0}+W\left(A+A^{+}\right) \tag{1}
\end{equation*}

In this expression, $A \equiv \sum_{n=1}^{N}|n\rangle\langle n+1|$, $A^{+} \equiv \sum_{n=1}^{N}|n+1\rangle\langle n|$, and we have the relationships

\[
\begin{array}{ll}
A|n\rangle=|n-1\rangle, & A^{+}|n\rangle=|n+1\rangle \\
