a & = \frac{\hbar^{2}}{Z m e^{2}} = \frac{m_{\mathrm{e}}}{Z m} \cdot \frac{\hbar^{2}}{m_{\mathrm{e}} e^{2}} = \frac{0.5}{13 \times 105} \times 0.53\ \mathrm{\AA} = 1.9 \times 10^{-4}\ \mathrm{\AA}
