& = \frac{\mathrm{e}^{2 k^{\prime} t} + \mathrm{e}^{-2 k^{\prime} t} - 2}{\mathrm{e}^{2 k^{\prime} t} + \mathrm{e}^{-2 k^{\prime} t} - 2 \cos 4 \theta}
\end{aligned}
\]

Where

\[
k^{\prime} = \sqrt{2mE} \sin \theta / \hbar
\]

The occupation numbers of the two eigenfunctions closest to the eigenfunction with an occupation number of 3 are 2 and 4, with the wave functions given by

